flowchart LR
    CLI[CLI command mode]
    ALIAS[Compatibility alias]
    HELPER[Inherited subordinate helper]
    CMC[Command mutation contract\nexisting reviewed authority extension]
    AUTH[Existing authority family\nregistry / lifecycle / state / workflow / evidence / migration / retention]
    GEN[Generator orchestration]
    LIFE[Existing document lifecycle]
    R1[Renderer: target A]
    R2[Renderer: target B]
    T1[Target A write + target-scoped acceptance]
    T2[Target B write + target-scoped acceptance]
    SEC[Declared secondary effects]
    PATH[Plan-bound changed-path verifier]
    AGG[Derived aggregate attempt result\nnon-authoritative]
    REC[Bounded orchestration recovery identity\nreferences per-target outcomes]
    RESULT[Command result]

    CLI --> CMC
    ALIAS --> CMC
    HELPER -. inherits without broadening .-> CMC
    CMC --> AUTH
    CMC --> GEN
    GEN --> LIFE
    LIFE --> R1
    LIFE --> R2
    R1 --> LIFE
    R2 --> LIFE
    LIFE --> T1
    LIFE --> T2
    GEN --> SEC
    T1 --> AGG
    T2 --> AGG
    SEC --> AGG
    T1 --> PATH
    T2 --> PATH
    SEC --> PATH
    PATH --> RESULT
    AGG --> RESULT
    AGG -. partial or failed .-> REC
    REC -. references; does not replace .-> T1
    REC -. references; does not replace .-> T2

    note1[No DPA command registry]
    note2[No aggregate acceptance state or trust state]
    note3[No second lifecycle or writer service]
    CMC --- note1
    AGG --- note2
    LIFE --- note3
